name: Dinari CSCO
description: The Dinari CSCO dShares token (CSCO.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in Cisco Systems, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSCO), a global leader in networking and IT infrastructure. Each CSCO.d token is fully backed by a corresponding Cisco stock share, securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, CSCO.d provides investors with exposure to Cisco's equity through a regulated financial product, offering benefits such as 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
